WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.600 --> 00:00:02.800
Do you know it's dangerous for you to do this?

2
00:00:02.933 --> 00:00:04.566
There are our messages outside.

3
00:00:04.566 --> 00:00:06.833
Don't you care about your reputation at all?

4
00:00:06.966 --> 00:00:08.000
Except for your injury

5
00:00:08.300 --> 00:00:09.200
I don't care about anything.

6
00:00:09.200 --> 00:00:10.000
Love

7
00:00:10.400 --> 00:00:11.633
But I care.

8
00:00:15.533 --> 00:00:17.166
Mr. Lu, we are here

9
00:00:18.500 --> 00:00:20.400
Wait for me soon

10
00:00:25.866 --> 00:00:27.300
That's it.

11
00:00:27.566 --> 00:00:28.666
Who are you?

12
00:00:28.666 --> 00:00:31.300
This is the set, you can't enter casually

13
00:00:31.300 --> 00:00:33.000
What are you doing? This is the break room

14
00:00:33.000 --> 00:00:33.933
Director Zhang is inside

15
00:00:33.933 --> 00:00:35.500
Director Zhang is an international director

16
00:00:35.500 --> 00:00:37.300
You can't enter without an appointment.

17
00:00:39.533 --> 00:00:41.700
Director Zhang, then say yes.

18
00:00:41.700 --> 00:00:43.466
The next movie has more

19
00:00:45.900 --> 00:00:46.700
Lu Xue

20
00:00:47.066 --> 00:00:48.100
What are you doing here?

21
00:00:48.100 --> 00:00:49.533
Are you tripping again?

22
00:00:49.533 --> 00:00:50.966
Do you know what a movie is?

23
00:00:50.966 --> 00:00:52.800
Director Zhang's work is art

24
00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:55.000
Art is not stupid like you

25
00:00:55.000 --> 00:00:57.666
The stinky capitalists can control

26
00:01:02.400 --> 00:01:04.300
Senior brother

27
00:01:04.400 --> 00:01:07.666
Brother, you returned to China to inherit the road

28
00:01:07.866 --> 00:01:09.233
What a pity!

29
00:01:09.300 --> 00:01:10.800
We went to school together

30
00:01:10.800 --> 00:01:12.400
The choreographer said it all

31
00:01:12.400 --> 00:01:14.900
You are the most talented student he has ever seen

32
00:01:15.066 --> 00:01:18.200
Why did I suddenly quit the European and American director circles?

33
00:01:18.200 --> 00:01:19.566
So now you know

34
00:01:19.700 --> 00:01:21.500
Why did I give up directing? Is it for you?

35
00:01:21.500 --> 00:01:22.300
Zeng Zeng

36
00:01:24.300 --> 00:01:27.266
Because capital can protect the people I want to protect

37
00:01:27.266 --> 00:01:28.633
Capital can be used at will

38
00:01:29.133 --> 00:01:30.500
You hurt him today

39
00:01:30.700 --> 00:01:31.866
I will give you tenfold

